Sentencas: Nonagglomerated strontium-doped lanthanum chromite powders were prepared by a modified Pechini resin-intermediate process and tape cast to form bipolar plates for a planar solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: TAPE CASTING AND SINTERING OF STRONTIUM-DOPED LANTHANUM CHROMITE FOR A PLANAR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL BIPOLAR PLATE

Sentencas: An air-sintering technique for the strontium-doped lanthanum chromite was developed, which involved placing the green tape between Cr2O3-fired plates.
Titulo: TAPE CASTING AND SINTERING OF STRONTIUM-DOPED LANTHANUM CHROMITE FOR A PLANAR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL BIPOLAR PLATE

Sentencas: The sintering process was found to be diffusion controlled, with densification beginning at the surface and proceeding to the interior.
Titulo: TAPE CASTING AND SINTERING OF STRONTIUM-DOPED LANTHANUM CHROMITE FOR A PLANAR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL BIPOLAR PLATE

Sentencas: A bipolar plate of 2-mm thickness was fired to more than 93.5% theoretical density when fired at 1670-degrees-C for 7 h.
Titulo: TAPE CASTING AND SINTERING OF STRONTIUM-DOPED LANTHANUM CHROMITE FOR A PLANAR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL BIPOLAR PLATE
